<template>
  <VehiclesDisplay :carList=""/>
</template>

<script>
import VehiclesDisplay from '../components/VehiclesDisplay.vue'
import {mapGetters} from 'vuex'

export default {




  components:{
    VehiclesDisplay,
  },
  computed: {
    ...mapGetters('vehicles', [
      "vehiclesList"
    ]),
    electricCars() {
    return this.vehiclesList.filter(x => x.fuel == 'electric')
  }
}

}
</script>

<style>

</style>
